{"id":759,"date":"2024-02-27T06:54:28","date_gmt":"2019-11-27T06:54:28","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/tv-wall-design-ideas-for-your-home\/"},"modified":"2023-09-01T19:04:29","modified_gmt":"2023-09-01T13:34:29","slug":"tv-wall-design-ideas-for-home","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/tv-wall-design-ideas-for-home\/","title":{"rendered":"TV Wall Design Ideas For Your Home"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p><em>TV wall designs that are going to make every movie or show an experience of a lifetime<\/em><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>TV units these days, especially for millennials, are amped up with sleek wall designs. Binge-watching is no longer something they do slouching on any old couch or on a laptop. Designs are in plenty and possibilities to get creative are limitless. The only thing you need to be mindful of is the space required to fit all accessories and components that come along with TV sets.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>For instance level screens, plasma or LED TVs, occupy less space and can be mounted on the wall easily without disrupting much. Nonetheless, your living room or bedroom wall can be designed and embellished with the right materials, decor elements, textures and colours to make TV viewing a craving you can\u2019t get enough of. So let us get started with the top ideas for TV wall design, shall we?<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-embed is-type-video is-provider-youtube wp-block-embed-youtube wp-embed-aspect-16-9 wp-has-aspect-ratio\"><div class=\"wp-block-embed__wrapper\">\n<iframe title=\"Watch these Cool TV Unit Ideas for Living Room | Modern TV Unit Design Ideas by Design Cafe\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" src=\"https:\/\/www.youtube.com\/embed\/iVCkTF09FxU?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share\" referrerpolicy=\"strict-origin-when-cross-origin\" allowfullscreen><\/iframe>\n<\/div><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Surround With Storage- TV Wall Idea For Living Room&nbsp;<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Surrounding your television with built-in storage solves two problems at once \u2013 you create a convenient spot for some of your most prized possessions and you can frame your TV with shelves of just the right size. Place your TV on a long cabinet that extend the length of your <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/living-room-design\/\">living room<\/a>. Cabinets have adequate room to store books, extra cables, crockery or anything else you may need to tuck away. Square shelves surround this TV bringing in pops of colour to this particular setting. A light coloured shelving unit such as this with cabinets on one side, drawers below, and open shelves on the other side adds much needed oomph to this living room.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/17060128\/tv-wall-ideas-for-living-room-to-solve-your-problems-1024x1024.jpg\" alt=\"TV Wall design idea for living room with built in storage which creates a spot for your valuable items\" class=\"wp-image-1474\"\/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Surrounding your television with built-in storage solves two problems at once.<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Make a statement with these modular tv unit for your homes interiors\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/15142955\/make-a-statement-with-these-modular-tv-unit-for-your-homes-interiors.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Frames Are Stunning Wall Design Ideas For Halls<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Framing your television with a background makes your television set stand out. Not only this, it also looks like it is exactly where it belongs. These frames also add to the overall decor of halls making it the cynosure of your home. Wooden frames, in particular blend in well considering several pieces of furniture in your hall will be made from this material. Now isn\u2019t this a simple yet superb TV wall design idea for a hall?<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/17060127\/wall-design-ideas-for-your-hall-1024x1024.jpg\" alt=\"Stunning TV wall design ideas for halls with dome shaped frames\" class=\"wp-image-1475\"\/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Dome shaped frames highlight your TV unit with dollops of desi class<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Recess It Into The Wall<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A simple yet classy TV wall design is mounting your screen on a textured wall. So a stone wall for example brings in some charm to an otherwise dull room and makes a subtle statement too. This wall design idea also does not steal the thunder of other elements in your room &#8211; decor, furniture, rugs or more. Your TV screen will look like it\u2019s sitting proudly on a gallery wall&nbsp; even when turned off! Marvelous idea we say!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/17060126\/LED-tv-mounted-on-a-textured-wall-1024x1024.jpg\" alt=\"A Textured TV wall design with led tv mounted on it to enhance the beauty of a room\" class=\"wp-image-1476\"\/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">LED TV screen mounted on a textured wall enhances the beauty of a room<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Make It The Centre of Attention<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Making your TV the focal point of a living room or bedroom with minimal decor surrounding it is a design idea most homeowners love. This is an extraordinary method to show off your TV on the wall without creating too much distraction. It keeps the structure basic and eliminates interruptions as you watch your favourite shows. TV sets therefore become a point of convergence in any room where friends and family congregate.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/17060124\/make-tv-wall-a-center-of-attraction-for-living-and-bedroom-1024x1024.jpg\" alt=\"TV wall design with some decor pieces which acts as a focal point for the living room\" class=\"wp-image-1477\"\/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A TV unit with some decor pieces around it make it stand out<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Also, Read About&nbsp;<a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/living-room-interiors\/living-room-wall-decor-ideas\/\">Living Room Wall Decor Ideas<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Balance A TV Screen On Your Bedroom Wall<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Now if you live in a small home or your bedroom is tiny you may not have space to build big, bulky storage cabinets around your TV unit. Smaller cabinets might just do the trick and give your TV wall design a unique look. Thin racks below your TV screen is a wonderful wall design idea for bedrooms. This especially if you want a spotless contemporary look and a spot to hold your things!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/17060123\/lcd-tv-screen-around-the-cabnits-1024x1024.jpg\" alt=\"Bedroom TV wall design with bulky storage cabinets and thin racks below your TV screen\" class=\"wp-image-1478\"\/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Racks under the television give your bedroom a spotless look<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Make The Most Of Materials For TV Wall Design Ideas<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Various materials yield out different television wall design ideas. Also, certain materials can look completely unique depending on how they are used. Wood is by far the most popular choice, more so with contemporary <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/\">home interior<\/a> designs. Marble, bricks or stones can all be used to make that exceptional TV wall design idea. Try marble on the backdrop of a TV screen instead of the floor &#8211; sounds funky? Well it certainly is. The sheen of this material lends a classy and subtle look. Bricks or stone bring in rustic elements. All in all they make your TV standout with panache raising the luxury quotient of your living room, bedroom or hall.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/17060122\/Led-tv-with-marble-designed-in-your-bedroom-1024x1024.jpg\" alt=\"Marble TV wall design ideas for your home for a classy and subtle look\" class=\"wp-image-1479\"\/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Marble works wonders for TV wall design and decor<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"End-to-end home interior design solutions for a stunning home\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/08180939\/end-to-end-home-interior-design-solutions-for-stunning-home.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Decor On Walls&nbsp;<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Creative, beautiful to look at and pretty darn interesting &#8211; decor on walls as a design idea sizzles up your room several notches. It is a particularly creative approach to feature your television as the showstopper of your room. Paint the wall a solid colour, put up some eclectic artwork and build some racks below &#8211; all these visual elements together make it a good mix of fun and fashionable living!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/17060121\/add-decor-to-your-tv-wall-design-1024x1024.jpg\" alt=\"TV wall decor which adds creativity to the TV wall and sizzles up your room\" class=\"wp-image-1480\"\/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Decor adds creativity to TV wall designs<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Explore, More About<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/living-room-interiors\/living-room-showcase-designs\/\">Living Room Showcase Designs<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/living-room-interiors\/wallpaper-designs-for-living-room\/\">Wallpaper Designs For Living Rooms<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/living-room-interiors\/best-tv-cabinet-design-ideas-for-living-room\/\">Best TV Cabinet Design Ideas For Living Room<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/living-room-interiors\/tv-unit-design-ideas-for-living-room\/\">7 Stylish TV Unit Design Ideas For Living Room<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend align=\"left\"> -->\n                    \n    <h3 class=\"widget-title text-dark text-center mb-0\">Looking For Functional Interior Designs?<\/h3>\n  \n \n     <p class=\"text-center text-dark mt-0\"> Get 20% extra space with smart solutions<\/p>\n    <!-- <\/legend> -->\n<form id=\"blogContactUsFormMain\" action=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/get_quote_action.php\" method=\"post\"\n    novalidate=\"novalidate\">\n    <div class=\"form-group\">\n        <input type=\"text\" class=\"form-control\"  name=\"your-name\" placeholder=\"Enter your name*\" \/>\n        <!-- <span class=\"sales-txt-label\" id=\"labeltxt\">Enter your name*<\/span>  -->\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"form-row dc-falg-row\">\n        <!-- <div class=\"form-group col-md-3 guideForm\">\n            <select name=\"your-phone-ext\" id=\"id_s